478
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:41,170
Who wouldn't like this kind of Little Sheep, right?

479
00:33:41,170 --> 00:33:45,800
I doubt it. I don't think Tang Xue is into the underage type.

480
00:33:45,800 --> 00:33:48,330
