496
00:34:25,730 --> 00:34:28,240
Think about it on your own.

497
00:34:28,240 --> 00:34:31,450
Ponder it for a while. I'm hanging up. Bye-bye.

498
00:34:31,450 --> 00:34:32,890
Hey–

499
00:34:37,210 --> 00:34:40,990
Listen, how heavy is this brow?

500
