510
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:15,250
What'd you say?

511
00:35:15,250 --> 00:35:18,180
I like Li Yubing.

512
00:35:19,730 --> 00:35:24,500
Do you have a death wish? Hurry up. Analyze it for me.

513
00:35:25,490 --> 00:35:29,750
